Twice a year, The Business Show: Africa elevates into a 3-day frenzy of business success webinars, incredible interactive exhibits, in-depth success insights and off the chart world class networking – all in an amazing virtual environment.The Business Show: Africa will be hosted virtually from 02 – 04 March 2022 and includes:Live WebinarsDelegates will get amazing insights from business leaders, experts, and entrepreneurs on a variety of business topics in live and interactive Q&A sessions, workshops, and panel discussions.Click here to see the full programme and book your sessions.Virtual B2B NetworkingMaximise on this gathering of like-minded, successful entrepreneurs, business leaders and potential partners and funders by joining our unique and inspired online networking sessions.Online ExhibitionDelegates will be able to access the best tools, services and expert advice at Solution Central, where you can browse through top class interactive exhibits. For the first time ever, the event will also include a live Virtual Exhibition Hall where you can move around the venue and interact with experts from leading solution providers in a live video chat.  Our build-up to the ultimate virtual experience starts today. So, over the next few weeks, look out for key announcements, guest speakers, and how you can get the most out of this experience.Your free passport gives you unlimited access to The Business Show: Africa 2022. To get your passport now go to www.thebizshow.africa and book your sessions here.